Package com.nokia.maps.common

The common package provides basic classes used by other packages in the JavaME Location API.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ConnectionListener
    This interface informs the connection of network connection events.
    GeoArea
    This interface defines a basis for classes which specify a geographic area.
    Location Deprecated
    use Location
    Place Deprecated
    use Place
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Address Deprecated
    use Address.
    ApplicationContext
    This class is used to configure application-wide information, such as authentication and language settings.
    ConnectionMonitor
    This class collections information and statistics about network activity.
    Contact Deprecated
    use Contacts
    GeoBoundingBox
    This class represents a rectangular area in a geographic coordinate system.
    GeoBoundingCircle
    This class defines a circular area in a geographic coordinate system.
    GeoCoordinate
    This class represents a geographical position.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description

    Common error for controllers.
